F75 Clinical Trial Analysis

Your Name

2024-12-02

Overview

This report summarizes the analyses performed on the F75 Clinical Trial dataset. The analyses focus on: - Baseline characteristics of participants. - Outcomes such as days to stabilization and discharge status. - Secondary outcomes, including mortality, adverse events, and changes in MUAC and weight.

Data and Methods

The data were analyzed using the following scripts: - analysis_baseline.R for baseline characteristics. - analysis_outcome1.R for primary outcomes. - analysis_outcome2.R for secondary outcomes.

Baseline Characteristics

The baseline analysis examines participants’ demographics and clinical status.
